{"tid":2452802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"冇諗過發生係我身上","createTime":"2021-03-19T05:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T12:32:31.000Z","uid":146697,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce2e56601ae40ed933510ddf68c97e0a245082d","tid":2452802,"uid":146697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"真係好辛苦 萬萬想唔到佢同其他男人私約，<br />\n我望唔哂佢手機d對話，因為好多。內容我唔太多講，總之有出過去啦。<br />\n我信佢只係朋友。<br />\n由2月開始隱暪我，佢果時唔太理我，我已經覺得古怪。<br />\n3月份好左好多 大家變親密左。<br />\n但諗起2果時 我覺得自已成個傻仔咁 咁信佢。<br />\n我信佢冇野，但無法接受隱瞞。<br />\n唔知仲有冇其他野暪隱我。<br />\n<br />\n各位有冇遇過咁既事，點樣去平靜自已，點樣處理？<br />\n我內心一諗起隱瞞我，真係好唔開心。"},{"pid":"58724f0af26d1f6d01fbf3121b93cfe28d3a68ed","tid":2452802,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"咩出過去 up乜"},{"pid":"356a80896b55734303548cdf509edb8822d84d24","tid":2452802,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"私約係食飯定開房先"},{"pid":"d7b9394811311c9f862dc3243c2f27a7189fb47b","tid":2452802,"uid":287107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"356a80896b55734303548cdf509edb8822d84d24","tid":2452802,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"私約係食飯定開房先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"扑野啦緊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39ec095af589fd5c8c96da8e054028cb7171032","tid":2452802,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b9394811311c9f862dc3243c2f27a7189fb47b","tid":2452802,"uid":287107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"356a80896b55734303548cdf509edb8822d84d24","tid":2452802,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"私約係食飯定開房先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"扑野啦緊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:17:20.000Z","m